## Project Description
 A responsive web application built with modern technologies to deliver a smooth and user-friendly experience.
Personal portfolio website showcasing my projects, technical skills, and contact information.

## Technologies Used
-HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript (ES6+)
React.js 

## Features
:General Web Application
: Portfolio Website
: Task Management App

1. Clone this repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
   OR
   Run `npm install` then `npm start`

## Lessons Learned
How to deploy a web application to a production environment
Managing environment variables and configuration settings
Fixing deployment and build errors
Connecting frontend and backend in a live environment
Improving website performance and optimization
Handling real-world bugs after deployment
Understanding domain hosting and live URL setup

## Challenges Faced
Resolving deployment errors during production build
Fixing environment variable configuration issues
Solving CORS issues between frontend and backend
Debugging errors that appeared only after deployment

